{
  "stem": "26792.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I have trod on something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I think-- yeah?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he answered me in Russian, [NON-ENGLISH]-- if you really ask me, we will arrest you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So, he saw a stupid, naive person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what the Soviet system is like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know anything what they're able to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was something new to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A long time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember how many months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, I-- on the first of May, my friends came to my house-- friends.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought Grishe, my present husband, with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Vaboulis was still in jail at that time?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He still was and remained, and there was no hope he would get out of jail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was accused of [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] being a traitor of his homeland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, it was changed-- the code was changed to anti-Soviet propaganda.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we were already husband and wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we got married in August of '45, and that was already [? forty ?] summer-- it was the first of May, 1946.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So my friends came to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had just had a cup of coffee or some-- a glass of wine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I sometimes went out with Grishe, but we were just on friendly terms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not on too friendly terms, just acquaintances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I could speak German and speak Yiddish and about, you know, Jewish questions, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they were-- then they started persecuting-- persecuting me in a terrible way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Calling me, summoning me to the KGB very often, even over the nights, and questioning me, investigating about things I had never seen and heard of.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
